This paper is primarily focused on text retrieval systems and inverted indexing, which are core topics in information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses memory hierarchies and processor architectures, which are relevant to data structures (cs.DS) and database systems (cs.DB). The paper also touches on performance evaluation (cs.CR) and algorithm design (cs.SE).
